  About 800 grams of heroin with a street value of 170,000 
schillings were smuggled by a Tirolian couple from Zurich to 
Vorarlberg since August. On Sunday [26 December], the 
25-year-old man and his 32-year-old girlfriend were arrested at 
the Lustenau border crossing. 

