hiding places of the yacht Gypsy Falcon, sailing under the 
British flag. The officials of Khania Customs Department 
believe that shocking things will be found as the ghost yacht is 
inspected completely. 
  The hashish, which was very carefully packed in 1-kg and 
2-kg 
cakes as well as in the form of tiles, was being taken by stages 
this morning by small trucks to safe storage at the Customs 
Department. 
  (Marco Ribic), 50, of Dubrovnik, who was the captain of the 
yacht and engineer (Denis Vitmar), 39, of Zagreb in the former 
Yugoslavia, who were the only two persons aboard the yacht, have 
been arrested and will probably be arraigned before the Khania 
prosecutor tomorrow. 
  According to reports, the yacht sailed from Yemen and 
through 
the Suez Canal was heading for Slovenia. However, because of 
engine trouble, it sailed into Khania port three days ago. 

