  [Text] Genoa, Italy, Jan 14 (AFP) -- Police Friday [14 
January] said they had arrested 23 Italians, including one who 
made a spectacular break from a U.S. jail, on suspicion of 
running heroin from Turkey and cocaine from Colombia. 
  They were said to be part of a 70-strong gang linked to the 
