<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Turkish </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Excerpt] The security forces have impounded 4,200 kg of 
hashish in a Kurdish Workers Party hideout in the Yikik Kopru 
locality near Uzumcu in Hakkari Province. The narcotics were 
discovered during the search operations in Hakkari's rural 
areas. [passage omitted] 

