<H3> <TI>   Narcotics Teams Seize 31 Kg of Heroin in Istanbul </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  TA0801205194 Ankara ANATOLIA in English 1520 GMT 7 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> TA0801205194 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara ANATOLIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Istanbul, Dec.7 (AA) -- In an operation here, 
narcotic teams have seized 31 kilos heroin. Five persons were 
detained in relation to the narcotic. 
  A statement by the narcotics department of the Security 
Directorate said today that, teams acting on a tip-off, carried 
out an operation to the home of Aziz Celik in the Gungoren 
district of Istanbul. 
  The narcotic was found in Celik's home. 
  His interrogation led to the seizure of Makhial Altan, Kamil 
Yakut, Celimhan Capa and Naif Bayhan. 
  Investigation into the case is expanded. 

</TEXT>

